{
  "stem": "25834.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I give watch, I give some gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Some, I keep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after, we go through the bathroom, or through the bath, and we receive new-- new other dress, we meet this guy together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And this guy give me back watch, what I not expect.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And give me the other stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I said, listen, watch, I take, because for me, it's memory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The other, you keep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this moment-- from this moment, start good relationship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And this guy give-- has good reputation there, and was on the position-- can do something for me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Working for hospital.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Prepare for me the job in [NON-ENGLISH], mean in a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Where you make, you know, wood, carpentry shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was very good, because one of the best was on the top barrack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Because the barracks was on the side of the mountain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And was 150 steps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And the barrack was at the top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "That was good, because German not like go there so often.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And listen again-- I was working there maybe two weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And one day, from transport, people who came from Hungary, was bring to our carpentry shop couple boxes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Like years ago, poor people has not suitcases like we have-- it was wood suitcases.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And also something what has to do with the wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And you know German-- never throw out what is useful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the old wood what was there, and plywood, was sent to our shop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And what happened-- I was there the youngest there. in the-- There was a couple Russian officers, because it was [INAUDIBLE] officers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And German-- German people who were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I was the guy who is supposed to cook in the can, like this, potato, and to watch through the window if SS man not going in.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
